rows.label: qev092709_MSG0010
rows.name: Wow... I guess Mira really does have its moments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0020
rows.name:
You've been up to your neck in work for so long,
you never had time to see the sights.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0040
rows.name:
Guess I didn't know what I'd been missing.
I was always leaving the field tests to you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0050
rows.name:
And I'm glad you did.
Working on Hraesvelg has been a dream.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0060
rows.name:
Remember that I'm the ace pilot here.
No arguing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0070
rows.name: Still thinking about what the boss said?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0090
rows.name:
Alicia. That guy would sell his
own grandma to turn a profit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0120
rows.name:
The path we've followed...
We've always walked it with conviction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0150
rows.name: The path that we must never stray from...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092709_MSG0170
rows.name:
Not now, not ever. We'll stick to our guns.
No matter what that crook says.[ST:wait ]
